### Project Overview
This is the week 4 project for the data science practical machine learning.  Per the request in the assignment, gh-pages were created for the repo.  An HTML page was knitted, and the RMD was uploaded to the repo as well.  You can download all files in the repo, or go directly to the repo by clicking on the links in the left.  If all you want to see is the html file, click here:

http://study-lsc.github.io/ml-week4-project.html
